*truecrypt-7.1 (07 Dec 2011)

  07 Dec 2011; Dane Smith <c1pher@gentoo.org> -truecrypt-7.0a-r2.ebuild,
  -truecrypt-7.0a-r5.ebuild, -truecrypt-7.0a-r6.ebuild, +truecrypt-7.1.ebuild:
